library(fixest)
Code 
wp_test <-
  read_rds(
    file.path(
      path_box,
      "Data",
      "WaterPointCensus",
      "DataSets",
      "Constructed",
      "wp-chlorine.rds"
    )
  ) %>%
  rename_with(
    ~ .x %>% 
      str_replace_all("meter", "meter_") %>% 
      str_replace_all("disc", "disc_") %>%
      str_replace_all("cr_c$", "cr")
  ) %>%
  dplyr::filter(!is.na(country), !is.na(disc_fcr))

3.1 Color wheel and colorimeter readings

Code 
wp_test %>%
  select(wp_id, matches("(.)cr$")) %>%
  pivot_longer(
    cols = -wp_id,
    names_pattern = "(.*)_(.*)",
    names_to = c(".value", "test")
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    test = str_to_upper(test)
  ) %>%
  ggplot(
    aes(
      x = meter,
      y = disc,
      color = test
    )
  ) +
  geom_abline(
    slope = 1,
    color = "gray80"
  ) +
  geom_abline(
    slope = 1,
    intercept = 0.2,
    color = "gray80",
    linetype = "dashed"
  ) +
  geom_abline(
    slope = 1,
    intercept = -0.2,
    color = "gray80",
    linetype = "dashed"
  ) +
  geom_abline(
    slope = 1,
    color = "gray80"
  ) +
  geom_point(position = "jitter") +
  theme +
  facet_wrap(~ test) +
  labs(
    x = "Colorimeter reading (mg/L)",
    y = "Color wheel reading (mg/L)",
    color = NULL
  ) + 
  scale_color_viridis_d()

3.2 TCR and FCR readings

Code 
wp_test %>%
  select(wp_id, matches("_(.)cr$")) %>%
  pivot_longer(
    cols = -wp_id,
    names_pattern = "(.*)_(.*)",
    names_to = c("test", ".value")
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    test = case_when(test == "meter" ~ "Colorimeter", TRUE ~ "Color wheel")
  ) %>%
  rename(
    TCR = tcr,
    FCR = fcr
  ) %>%
  ggplot(
    aes(
      x = FCR,
      y = TCR,
      color = test
    )
  ) +
  geom_abline(
    slope = 1,
    color = "gray80"
  ) +
  geom_abline(
    slope = 1,
    intercept = -0.1,
    color = "gray80",
    linetype = "dashed"
  ) +
  geom_abline(
    slope = 1,
    intercept = -0.2,
    color = "gray80",
    linetype = "dotted"
  ) +
  geom_abline(
    slope = 1,
    color = "gray80"
  ) +
  geom_point(position = "jitter") +
  theme +
  facet_wrap(~ test) +
  scale_color_viridis_d() +
  theme(legend.position = "none")
